description:
Guy #1: Corey, 25, 5'10", 200

Guy #2: Kevin, 24, 6'1", 170

Kevin got out of the Air Force a while ago and was looking to do something different.

When he came in for his audition, I noticed he had a cut on his lip. I asked him about it and he told me he had been in a fight two days earlier with a guy who was bothering his girlfriend.
title: Auditions 4
